precis:
Authority for the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into
(a) Enhanced Matching Contribution Agreements for the NISA PROGRAM with
NOVA SCOTIA, ONTARIO, QUEBEC, PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND and NEWFOUNDLAND, and
